messages.message:
Issue due to Barcode and Pillow version conflict. SC installed PDFPlumber package which had Pillow dependency due to which latest version of PILLOW got installed.

Barcode version 11 does not support Pillow version >7. We are providing new patch with Pillow version 7.1.0 . Path forward will be have Barcode version 13 and Pillow version >8
